Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:23.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:30.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:48.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:55.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:01:02.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:10.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:13.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:17.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:21.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:24.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:32.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:35.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:39.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:43.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:55.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never give up on this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys stupid or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably got fooled by the shipwrights'\Nconvincing argument, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Luffy I know would've believed\Nin the strength of the Merry first
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than buying those guys' sales talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a clear-cut answer that sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like one made by an old man\Nwho understands everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you make a decision like that,\Nsuddenly acting all captain-like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I misjudged you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec, Usopp! Luffy, too, first--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this, Nami!\NThis is something I decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't change my opinion.\NNo matter what you say now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're gonna get a new ship!\NWe'll say goodbye to the Merry here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Luffy! It's not like everyone\Ncan live looking ahead like you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just leave our wounded friend\Nhere and move on to the seas ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! Even if she's a friend,\Nships and humans are different!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the same! Merry has\Nthe strength to live left in her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Considering how you are, aren't you\Nexcited thinking about the new ship\N--Hey, that's enough, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--while pretending to be concerned about Merry?!\N--You can't have a conversation\Nif you're worked up like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that you're the only\None who feels pain over this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone feels the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, there's no way you'd\Ndecide to get a new ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! If you dislike what I decide\Nthat much, then get off this--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot... What were you about to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool down! Be careful about what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, Luffy. That's how\Nyou really feel, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and cut off useless friends\None after another and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna abandon the Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why don't you do that to me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need weak friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... you're the man\Nwho'll be king of the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have to go that high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where're you going, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I'm going is my own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...leaving the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! It shouldn't be like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! I can't go along with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to cause you trouble until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the ship\Nbelongs to you, the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So fight me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight a duel with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At 10 o'clock tonight, I'll come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll fight a duel over the Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you and take the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the end of the bond\Nbetween you guys and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:51.49,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Luffy vs. Usopp! Collision of Two Men's Pride"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Usopp, leader of the great\Npirates who reign over this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People praise me-- and then praise\Nme more-- as "Captain Usopp"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a very proud man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my great pride,\Npeople call me "Proud Usopp"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys take care, too!\NLet's meet again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How come?\N--Huh? How come? Man, you're antisocial...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be a pirate too, so we'll\Nmeet on the high seas eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talkin' about? Get on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I get to be captain, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be dumb! I'm the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you didn't get cold feet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be sure you're not going\Nto regret this, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the duel you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. You'd better fight seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn the tables on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already figured out how to defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we stop them?\NUsopp is wounded quite badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't bear to watch this, go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lump me in with your past\Nenemies who didn't know your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... We've known each other for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about your powers very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be surprised when you hear this, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:08:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have 8,000 men under me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna die, surrender now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! 8,000?! That many?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any subordinates.\NI know that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got razors stuck between all your teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts just to imagine that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got cactus spines inside your fingernails!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?! His body is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack... Ketchup Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you sympathizing with\Nyour enemy? What confidence...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flash Dial!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack! Egg Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Star! Star! Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks! They're rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! You jerk! Be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this silly? I'm very serious, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--This is my way of fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you open your mouth\Nthat big, you'll have a burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack! Tabasco Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hooot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out when you wriggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath your feet, it's already Caltrop Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp is in control of the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you without fail and take the Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack! Pepper Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owwww!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. I won't use attacks\Nthat won't work on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. It stinks... My mouth is burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give you even the\Nslightest chance to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack! Shuriken Shooting Stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm using a Breath Dial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't notice the smell\Nbecause of the eggs, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of the gas that's\Nfilling the area around you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Usopp, leader of the great\Npirates who reign over this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People praise me-- and then praise\Nme more-- as "Captain Usopp"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Incredible! What kind of island is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry! Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... that an attack like\Nthat wouldn't take you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you fight every battle\Nwith all your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know every detail of your skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bursting Cactus Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triple Exploding Stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a dial here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got... your impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Impact Dial!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that?! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Usopp, leader of the great\Npirates who reign over this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To our new ship and crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good! Let's draw it on the sail, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the Going Merry pirate ship is all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that you\Ncould defeat me, is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want with the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get a new ship and\Nmove on to the seas ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let me sit there, too, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! This is my special seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you making, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Hey, you guys!\NNo shoes in Usopp Factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I will go to Elbaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the village of warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Usopp! Let's go there for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this party goin'! It's the\Nnight festival before gold-hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, bye, Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't go, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?! He was already\Nwounded so badly to start with,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now he got beat up worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a quarrel or a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?! I'm a doctor!\NLet me at least treat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lost the duel. On top of that, he gets pitied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine just how miserable\Nthat must make him feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine how much suffering careless\Nkindness can cause the loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fought a duel knowing full well\Nthis was how it might turn out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be a captain, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you waver, who can we trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's vacate the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't come back... to this ship, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:23.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:26.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:32.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:34.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:37.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:43.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:46.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:48.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:51.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:00.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:06.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:11.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:14.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:19.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, there's trouble! The whole\Ntown is talking about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's the matter?\N--They say that Iceberg-san was\Nshot at home and is unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice pops is?! I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll go, too.\N--Then, Chopper and I'll go look for Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.47,0:23:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Severe Shock Hits the City\Nof Water! Iceberg Targeted!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
